{"tid":722809,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"山寨版神奇女俠《精靈的後裔》！網民：抄都做吓功課","createTime":"2018-06-30T00:20:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T08:33:47.000Z","uid":66943,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"25c46003d69b9b96b7621d54df2a9f9b3dc50c54","tid":722809,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T00:20:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2105000/2105021/20180629_wonderwoman_01_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2105000%2F2105021%2F20180629_wonderwoman_01_1024.jpg&h=e11b83dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2105000/2105021/20180629_wonderwoman_02_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2105000%2F2105021%2F20180629_wonderwoman_02_600.jpg&h=4e79d693&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n常常都說中國人的創意無限，可以山寨的東西基本上都有能力「複製」過來，而最新的山寨產物，就是從 DC 漫畫《神奇女俠》而來的《精靈的後裔》。其實人們看中國山寨品，因為實在見得太多，所以基本上都見怪不怪，但山寨版神奇女俠《精靈的後裔》近日因為一個元素，成為網民瘋狂恥笑對象，就是《精靈的後裔》的導演一然是這樣介紹作品的：「影片創作的靈感最初就來自《神奇女俠》，雖然原本是個好萊塢漫威奇幻大片 ......」<br />\n<br />\n抄都做吓功課<br />\n<br />\nWell，這樣的介紹就出事了，因為有留意超級英雄漫畫、電影的朋友都知道，《神奇女俠》是 DC 作品，並不是源自漫威 Marvel，所以導演一然的介紹一出，立即被受恥笑，有香港網民轉發這段介紹，以及上載《精靈的後裔》女主角王崳的「神奇女俠造型」照片後，不忘表示：「抄都做下功課」、「神抄女俠」、「100 歲未死都有笑話聽」。另外有網民認為《精靈的後裔》是 X 到唔敢睇，「睇的價值都無，女主角成個呀嬸樣」、「呢啲垃圾啱晒大陸口味」、「畫面特效咁有 8、90 年代 feel」，的確很難鼓起勇氣看下去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2105000/2105021/20180629_wonderwoman_04_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2105000%2F2105021%2F20180629_wonderwoman_04_600.jpg&h=a1447373&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7 月 11 日首播<br />\n<br />\n假如大家想「挑戰極限」地一探《精靈的後裔》的虛實，不妨於 7 月 11 日開始在大陸影片分享網站優酷收看。至於故事內容方面，就是現為保安員，但夢想當警察的女主角項大麗（王崳飾），因一次執勤意外，獲得天外神力成為精靈的後裔。其後項大麗有一名自稱「關羽後人」的型男成為她的貼身護花使者，暗中幫其執行任務，而在一次任務中，項大麗被臨危受命，跟華聲（鄧皓飾）拍擋聯手尋找一名神秘豪二代（伍麟凱飾），不料過程中遇上強到不能的大反派黑衣人，展開一場充滿歷險過程的傳奇故事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2105000/2105021/20180629_wonderwoman_03_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2105000%2F2105021%2F20180629_wonderwoman_03_600.jpg&h=d5dc9afc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">網民看過《精靈的後裔》劇照，都有柒到唔敢睇的感覺，但當然大家如果想「挑戰極限」，不妨於 7 月 11 日開始在優酷網觀看。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國2025<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af9dbc536e473d24a188b31178de343be1348a8e","tid":722809,"uid":177089,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T00:23:26.000Z","msg":"superman? whatever"},{"pid":"8db2304a1efb99b98677f14bdbfccc342235b580","tid":722809,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T00:25:13.000Z","msg":"拍到連大陸人都覺得柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b9334af876c72a4d49ad94f0dd2475e6a98aed","tid":722809,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T00:27:27.000Z","msg":"如果開拍一套《精靈得後門》嘅愛情動作片 就正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc3badade8f5666108e576baf1dbc88f82261de","tid":722809,"uid":117602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0b9334af876c72a4d49ad94f0dd2475e6a98aed","tid":722809,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T00:27:27.000Z","msg":"如果開拍一套《精靈得後門》嘅愛情動作片 就正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"reply